              li Mix of BBB and Custom HW
              li Modified Fridge
              li All DIY

      section
        .fullscreen(ui-fx="blur2")
          x-gif(src="images/thinking_fred.gif" fill stopped ping-pong n-times="3")
        .content
          .box
